<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٧٤٥ - د ج ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دَجْل/ دَجَل <span class="c4">[مفرد]</span>:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - طريقة تصرُّف الدَّجّالين، والشَّائع فتح الجيم <span class="c1">"تنبَّه للدَّجْل"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢ - كذِب <span class="c1">"إيَّاك والدَّجَل في الحديث"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>